<h2>Reset Your Password</h2>

<p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

<p>We received a request to reset your password for your EventFlow account. If you made this request, use the code below to reset your password.</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">Your Reset Code</h3>
    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; font-family: monospace; color: #1e40af; margin: 20px 0;">
        {{resetCode}}
    </p>
    <p class="text-muted" style="text-align: center;">This code expires in {{expiryMinutes}} minutes</p>
</div>

<a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>

<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
    <span class="text-muted">Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</span><br>
    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="color: #1e40af; word-break: break-all; font-size: 12px;">{{resetUrl}}</a>
</p>

<div class="divider"></div>

<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #fee2e2; border-left-color: #dc2626;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #991b1b;">Security Notice</h3>
    <p><strong>Didn't request a password reset?</strong></p>
    <p>If you didn't make this request, your account may be at risk. Please take these steps:</p>
    <ul style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>Ignore this email (the reset link will expire automatically)</li>
        <li>Consider changing your password if you haven't recently</li>
        <li>Enable two-factor authentication for extra security</li>
        <li>Contact support if you notice any suspicious activity</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<h3 style="color: #1e40af;">Password Security Tips</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Use a strong, unique password (at least 8 characters)</li>
    <li>Include uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</li>
    <li>Don't reuse passwords from other websites</li>
    <li>Consider using a password manager</li>
    <li>Enable two-factor authentication for extra security</li>
</ul>

<p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 12px;">
    This password reset was requested from:<br>
    IP Address: {{ipAddress}}<br>
    Device: {{userAgent}}<br>
    Time: {{requestTime}}
</p>

<p class="text-muted">
    Need help? Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>
</p>
